text: Wismoyo Arismunandar (10 February 1940 â€“ 28 January 2021) was an Indonesian high-ranking Army officer. He was Army Chief of Staff from 1993 to 1995 and Commander of Army Strategic Command from 1990 to 1993. Arismunandar was born in Bondowoso, Dutch East Indies. Arismunandar died on 28 January 2021 in Jakarta, Indonesia at the age of 80. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Indonesian generals
